      • showNotes

        public static void showNotes​(java.awt.Window parent,
                             AbstractModel model,
                             AbstractComponent[] components,
                             java.lang.String[] shortNames)
        opens (or toFronts) the ALModelNotesFrame for the given model then sets the search criteria to display only those notes.
        Parameters:
        parent - the java.awt.Window parent to use for any dialogs displayed by this method.
        model - the AbstractModel that contains the components.
        components - an AbstractComponent[] the components for which to display notes
        shortNames - a String containing the "short name" of the attribute level documentation target for which notes should be shown.
